snippet.title: Scars Above Gameplay Trailer | Koch Media Primetime 2021
snippet.description: Scars Above is an upcoming 3rd person action shooter which will pit you against nightmarish creatures on an alien world. The game will give you multiple ways to survive the planet, including ways to craft and upgrade your weapons.
